8","julianDay":2206102,"title":"First War of Scottish Independence","description":"The First War of Scottish Independence began after England invaded Scotland in 1296. The Treaty of Edinburgh was signed in 1328 which declared peace between the two kingdoms and brought the war to an end.","jurisdictionLevel":1},{"id":1705193,"age":30,"year":"1337","toYear":"1453","julianDay":2209390,"title":"The Hundred Years' War","description":"The Hundred Years' War between France and England was largely due to the question of legitimate succession to the French crown.","jurisdictionLevel":1}],"lifeSummary":"When William de Septvans was born in 1307, in Kent, England, his father, William de Septvans I, was 27 and his mother, Elizabeth De Pympe, was 11304. He had at least 1 son with Elizabeth Darrell. He died in 1352, at the age of 45."},"et":{"1307–1352":"1307–1352","1310–Male":"1310–Surnud","1312–Male":"1312–Surnud","1314–Male":"1314–Surnud","1310–1356":"1310–1356","1346–1407":"1346–1407","1281–1323":"1281–1323","1281–Female":"1281–Surnud","1352":"1352","1281":"1281","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","1314":"1314","1346":"1346","1323":"1323","1356":"1356","1312":"1312","1300":"1300","1453":"1453","1310":"1310","1407":"1407","1307":"1307","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","Pimpe, Kent, England":"Kent, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Kent, England":"Kent, England"},"fi":{"1307–1352":"1307–1352","1310–Male":"1310–Kuollut","1312–Male":"1312–Kuollut","1314–Male":"1314–Kuollut","1310–1356":"1310–1356","1346–1407":"1346–1407","1281–1323":"1281–1323","1281–Female":"1281–Kuollut","1352":"1352","1281":"1281","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","1314":"1314","1346":"1346","1323":"1323","1356":"1356","1312":"1312","1300":"1300","1453":"1453","1310":"1310","1407":"1407","1307":"1307","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","Pimpe, Kent, England":"Kent, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Kent, England":"Kent, England"},"fr":{"1307–1352":"1307–1352","1310–Male":"1310–Décédé","1312–Male":"1312–Décédé","1314–Male":"1314–Décédé","